<h1>I-9 Verification Update</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @candidate.first_name %>,</p>

<p>
  Your I-9 employment eligibility verification for the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong>
  position at <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong> has been updated.
</p>

<h2>Status</h2>

<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #28a745;">
  <strong>Section 2 Complete</strong>
</p>

<p>
  Our HR team has reviewed and verified your identity and employment authorization documents.
  <% if @i9_verification&.status == "verified" %>
    Your I-9 verification is now complete.
  <% else %>
    We are finalizing your verification and will notify you once complete.
  <% end %>
</p>

<h2>What's Next</h2>

<% if @i9_verification&.status == "verified" %>
  <p>
    Your employment eligibility has been verified. You're all set to start work on
    <%= @i9_verification&.employee_start_date&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>!
  </p>
<% else %>
  <p>
    Your verification is being processed. You will receive another notification
    once it is fully complete.
  </p>
<% end %>

<p>
  If you have any questions about your I-9 verification or onboarding, please
  contact our HR team.
</p>

<p>
  Welcome to the team!
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  The <%= @organization.name %> HR Team
</p>
